==评价==
影片收获大量好评，[[烂番茄|烂番茄]]上有95%的新鲜度。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/nightcrawler/|title=Nightcrawler (2014)|website=Rotten Tomatoes|accessdate=2014-10-29|archive-date=2019-05-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190506164814/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/nightcrawler|dead-url=no}}</ref>[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]上45家媒体综评76分。<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/nightcrawler | title=Nightcrawler Reviews | work=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]] | publisher=[[CBS_Interactive|CBS Interactive]] | accessdate=2014-10-28 | archive-date=2018-02-01 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180201064602/http://www.metacritic.com/movie/nightcrawler | dead-url=no }}</ref>《[[洛杉矶时报|洛杉矶时报]]》给90分：这是一部设置聪明、剧情紧凑，以令人不安的现实为基础的情节剧，[[傑克·葛倫霍|傑克·葛倫霍]]的亮眼表演为影片的进展提供了动力。《[[今日美国|今日美国]]》给88分：减肥三十磅，颧骨高耸，双眼凸出，傑克·葛倫霍在这部黑暗而充满挑战性的作品中扮演了一个他职业生涯最令人印象深刻的角色。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.mtime.com/2014/11/03/1533492-2.html#content |title=《夜行者》与《死亡占卜》并列榜首 |access-date=2014-11-03 |archive-date=2018-01-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180127143322/http://news.mtime.com/2014/11/03/1533492-2.html#content |dead-url=no }}</ref>

